arts.ttl: Davitashvili hat trick leads Saint-Etienne past Auxerre in Ligue 1
arts.sum: Georgia international Zuriko Davitashvili scored a hat trick to lead struggling Saint-Etienne to its second win in the French league, 3-1 against Auxerre on Saturday. Davitashvili joined from Bordeaux this summer as Saint-Etienne prepared to return to the top-flight following a two-year absence.
